 width=\"1\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr itemprop=\"track\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/MusicRecording\">\r\n<td>9</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Synth (Hold Me)</td>\r\n<td width=\"25\"></td>\r\n<td width=\"1\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr itemprop=\"track\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/MusicRecording\">\r\n<td>10</td>\r\n<td></td>\r\n<td>Pipe Organ (Hold Me)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>','publish','open','closed','','pequena-fiera-%e2%80%8e-casiotone-for-bears','','','2013-09-11 21:44:22','2013-09-11 19:44:22','',0,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/?post_type=product&#038;p=211',0,'product','',0),(212,2,'2013-09-11 21:43:53','2013-09-11 19:43:53','','Gratuit - Délivrance','<div id=\":am.co\">\r\n<div id=\":aq.ma\">\r\n<div id=\":aq.co\">[bandcamp album=890967068 bgcol=FFFFFF linkcol=d52b2b size=grande2]</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\nAprès un hôtel désaffecté en Bretagne où il enregistrait « Rien », Gratuit trouve refuge dans une cabane de chasse dans les Pyrénées pour ululer « Délivrance ». Pour hurler à la mort, se vautrer, se maculer de cendre et de sang, peinard. Des invitées (Julia Lanoë,Françoiz Breut) le rejoignent, ça se barricade et ça expulse. Délivrance, sinon rien.\r\n\r\nQuand il ne s\'enferme pas, GRATUIT bricole. Musicien, performeur, artisan, poète, arrangeur, dérangeur, avec et sans pseudo, Antoine Gratuit Bellanger a ce goût du « faire avec ». Avec des gens, des lieux, des situations. On l\'a vu préparer des performances sonores à base de solénoïdes sur un bateau (Summerlab Gijon) ou dans un contener modulable (TRANS 305). On l\'a vu dans des squats et des musées s\'attaquer à des œuvres majeures, match de foot (France-RFA 82 avec H. Guilloteau et Rebeka Warrior) et peintures début XXème (au côté de Guillaume Marmin). On l\'a vu se foutre en l\'air sur le dance-floor à 19h02 et 03h28. On l\'a vu enregistrer et arranger des groupes comme Mansfield.Tya ou The Healthy Boy, remixer du Sexy Sushi et s\'acoquiner récemment avec Mein Sohn William.\r\n\r\nOn l\'aurait vu aussi dans le dernier Carax, à l\'arrière d\'une stretch limo conduite par Laurie Anderson filant sur la route Manset... L\'ex-Belone Quartet a travaillé sa noise mélancolique à la recherche de mélodies curieuses comme Yo La Tengo sait si bien le faire pour nous livrer des ballades version Daho du futur.Textes lapidaires, beats blessés, un songwriting minimal animal. Gratuit est bien de retour parmi les siens, parmi les chiens. (Qui se souviennent probablement de rien).\r\n<div id=\":am.co\">\r\n<div id=\":aq.ma\">\r\n<div id=\":aq.co\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','publish','open','closed','','gratuit-delivrance','','','2013-09-11 21:56:28','2013-09-11 19:56:28','',0,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/?post_type=product&#038;p=212',0,'product','',0),(213,2,'2013-09-11 21:42:41','2013-09-11 19:42:41','','ETW018_SIMULATION_RECTO_600','','inherit','open','open','','etw018_simulation_recto_600','','','2013-09-11 21:42:41','2013-09-11 19:42:41','',212,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/ETW018_SIMULATION_RECTO_600.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(214,1,'2013-09-11 21:42:58','2013-09-11 19:42:58','','pequena-fiera','','inherit','open','open','','pequena-fiera','','','2013-09-11 21:42:58','2013-09-11 19:42:58','',211,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/pequena-fiera.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(215,2,'2013-09-11 21:48:31','2013-09-11 19:48:31','',' Party Ruiners vol​.​4','[bandcamp album=3634631499 bgcol=FFFFFF linkcol=d52b2b size=grande2]\r\n\r\nQuelques mois seulement après la sortie de la Party Ruiners vol.3, Ego Twister records propose un nouveau volet de sa série de compilation. Le volume 4 ne délaisse pas le psychédélisme pop et synthétique, mais donne cette fois-ci dans le gothique d’opérette, le macabre factice et les fausses histoires de maisons hantées.\r\n\r\nOnze artistes, essentiellement français mais également suisses et espagnols, dont plusieurs fidèles au label depuis ses débuts, contribuent à ce puzzle musical intriguant, à l’image de la pochette déssinée par Marion Balac et qui ne porte aucune inscription. Il appartient à l’auditeur de reconstruire l’histoire racontée en filigrane par chacun de ces morceaux.\r\n\r\nL’éclectisme qui caractérise le label est toujours au rendez-vous, et cette Party Ruiners réaffirme son ambition de réunir des artistes aux influences les plus diverses dans une playlist cohérente. Dans l’ordre : bricolage lo-fi, fanfare jumpstyle, booty 8bit, chœurs synthétiques, techno pour de rire, electronica abrasive, new-wave glacée, electro hip hop épique, euroclash, punk digital, dance expérimentale.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','publish','open','closed','','party-ruiners-vol%e2%80%8b-%e2%80%8b4','','','2013-09-11 21:55:35','2013-09-11 19:55:35','',0,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/?post_type=product&#038;p=215',0,'product','',0),(216,1,'2013-09-11 21:52:22','2013-09-11 19:52:22','','Carton Sonore - Kind Regards from the Land of Wander','[bandcamp album=3394812705 bgcol=FFFFFF linkcol=d52b2b size=grande2]\r\n\r\nThis is how Carton Sonore sounds like as a band.\r\n\r\n///////////////////////////////////////////////////////\r\n\"Pour ensoleiller vos dimanches matins pluvieux\" - A Découvrir Absolument\r\n///////////////////////////////////////////////////////\r\n\"Une recette de cuisine au goût fruité\" - Foutraque\r\n///////////////////////////////////////////////////////\r\n\"C’est de la musique de chambre mais en bordel\" - Benzine Magazine\r\n///////////////////////////////////////////////////////\r\n\"Its like riding a bike towards the edge of a cliff on a sunny day\" - Paul Vickers (Dawn Of The Replicants)\r\n///////////////////////////////////////////////////////\r\n<h3>credits</h3>\r\n<div>released 15 May 2013\r\nPierre Ch: voice, charango, ukulele, musical saw, keyboard (track 9), noises\r\nPierre Ca: bass\r\nCorentin K: violin, keyboard, xylophone, maracas\r\nPauline B: toy piano, melodica, cello, glockenspiel\r\nGuillaume E: percussions\r\nAnne &amp; Gary: omnichord, strange voices (tracks 9 and 10)Mastered by Guillaume E\r\n\r\nRecorded in Paris, 2012\r\nReleased on MonsterK7 and With A Messy Head, 2013\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://monsterk7.com/catalogue/kind-regards-from-the-land-of-wander/\">http://monsterk7.com/catalogue/kind-regards-from-the-land-of-wander/</a>\r\n\r\n</div>','publish','open','closed','','carton-sonore-kind-regards-from-the-land-of-wander','','','2013-09-11 21:53:05','2013-09-11 19:53:05','',0,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/?post_type=product&#038;p=216',0,'product','',0),(217,2,'2013-09-11 21:46:57','2013-09-11 19:46:57','','ETW015_MARION_02','','inherit','open','open','','etw015_marion_02','','','2013-09-11 21:46:57','2013-09-11 19:46:57','',215,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/ETW015_MARION_02.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(218,2,'2013-09-11 21:53:59','2013-09-11 19:53:59','','[guÿôm] - Cacelorazo','[bandcamp album=1390695636  bgcol=FFFFFF linkcol=d52b2b size=grande2]\r\n\r\n\"Guyom is a monstertruckdriver on Planet Mu, a bass-thrower in line of dancefloorfire sparking weirdness and humour like there is no tomorrow. If you want to get the strobelight ready, better do it now. But to focus solely on the twisted and distorted beats, the iconoclastic and pounding rhythms and percussions, is taking it a step to little for Guyom. As is stated somewhere on the record, “cacelorazo” is also a word for banging pots and pans to create noise during protests and demonstrations. It started in Argentinia in 2001 and then made some headway into the global news for its news-worth. Like the whistles in Germany or the orange shawls in the Ukraine and nothing at all like happy slapping in the United Kingdom. The whistling soon was eaten up by mass techno and I don’t even want to talk about what the colour orange stands for now in Austrian politics (fucking right wing extremists…) and happy slapping is hopefully a trend gone by now. Guyom will be a lonely dancefloor dj when putting politics to obviously into the faces of partygoers, who at times prefer to have a spoon and nothing to eat to the vice versa situation, but he might make it up with his tracks. If the crowd is open minded to twisted rhythms and distorted sounds, that is, because he likes to take them to extremes, as on “contre ventes et marchés”, where he speeds up the keys and mixes them against a shitload of drums and idm breakbeats. (By the way, the label IDM has always seemed like an oxymoron to me, but so has most of the music labelling business anyway).\r\n\r\nBut maybe he is not at all about politics, but rather affected by the noise-side of the cacelorazo-kind of demonstration. A noisemaker and crowdmonger, a peace disturber and frantic dancefloor collaborator. I can see some of the bass sounds on this record destroying the concrete walls of clubs, which would add some truth to this assumption. And he likes to flaunt an equally twisted humour (especially during the hillbilly sequences at “Cart(o)on” and then some other places) that sometomes might seem to obvious. I have no idea how this works on dancefloors? Maybe it is too single-minded on a weird drum sequence and one added line of other sounds, though judging from what I know about idm/techno-parties, which is admittedly not very much, it might be too multi-layered for some of them. This definitely isn’t the bland four to the floor beat (though “Moody building” definitely goes into that direction, even perusing the swooshed in hand claps, but takes a detour by using a slew of different basic rhythms) and it is also not the refined and micro-distilled breakbeat stuff of the more academic circles. “Cacelorazo” keeps away from straightforwardness, smells home brewed and has the distinct flavor of a local speciality that comes from an inside will to create some noise and stirr the shit around. Guess that worked out fine.\r\n\r\nFrom time to time a record like this hits the Cracked home and if time and circumstances are right, it will be welcomed warmly and with a big hand. Examples would be Larytta (Creaked Records) or O.Lamm (Active Suspension). Thankfully Guyom had the same luck. Thanks for twisting our homeoffice dancefloor.\"\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','publish','open','closed','','guyom-cacelorazo','','','2013-09-11 21:53:59','2013-09-11 19:53:59','',0,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/?post_type=product&#038;p=218',0,'product','',0),(219,1,'2013-09-11 21:50:52','2013-09-11 19:50:52','','carton-sonore','','inherit','open','open','','carton-sonore','','','2013-09-11 21:50:52','2013-09-11 19:50:52','',216,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/carton-sonore.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(220,2,'2013-09-11 21:53:41','2013-09-11 19:53:41','','ETW007_POCHETTE_800x533','','inherit','open','open','','etw007_pochette_800x533','','','2013-09-11 21:53:41','2013-09-11 19:53:41','',218,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/ETW007_POCHETTE_800x533.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(221,1,'2013-09-11 22:00:33','2013-09-11 20:00:33','','Mother\'s Auxillary - Winter EP','[bandcamp album=581231736 bgcol=FFFFFF linkcol=d52b2b size=grande2]\r\n\r\nCet EP a été enregistré par le jeune musicien anglais Mother’s Auxillary avec l’aide des musiciens de son ancien projet musical The Appreciation Society. Douce et électronique, prête à déborder d’énergie mais gardant une touche folk touchante, la musique de Mother’s Auxillary lance un pont entre l’electronica et le folk.\r\n\r\n<b><b>Date de sortie :</b> 15 avril 2009</b>','publish','open','closed','','mothers-auxillary-winter-ep','','','2013-09-11 22:00:33','2013-09-11 20:00:33','',0,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/?post_type=product&#038;p=221',0,'product','',0),(222,2,'2013-09-11 22:01:17','2013-09-11 20:01:17','','Niwouinwouin - Troll slayer ','[bandcamp album=927432600 bgcol=FFFFFF linkcol=d52b2b size=grande2]\r\n\r\nAprès \"Catastrophe\", ode à une fin du monde fantasmée en forme de 45t, Niwouinwouin revient avec \"Troll slayer\". Ce nouvel hymne electro pop au tempo enlevé emmène le jeune musicien nantais encore un peu plus loin dans son exploration d\'un imaginaire enfantin débridé et sauvage. En face B de ce disque au format désuet, \"Man eater\" complète l\'épopée sur un ton plus inquiétant.\r\n\r\nUn clip d\'animation est actuellement en préparation en collaboration avec le frère de Niwouinwouin, l\'illustrateur Jean Jullien qui dirige également la direction artistique de ce disque. Ensemble, ils déjà ont réalisé le clip de \"Catastrophe\" et l\'installation-projection \"Adventures in the front of TV set\", ainsi que de nombreuses autres collaboration.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','publish','open','closed','','niwouinwouin-troll-slayer','','','2013-09-11 22:01:17','2013-09-11 20:01:17','',0,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/?post_type=product&#038;p=222',0,'product','',0),(223,2,'2013-09-11 21:59:39','2013-09-11 19:59:39','','ETW012_photo_600x359','','inherit','open','open','','etw012_photo_600x359-2','','','2013-09-11 21:59:39','2013-09-11 19:59:39','',222,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/ETW012_photo_600x3591.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(224,2,'2013-09-11 21:59:47','2013-09-11 19:59:47','','ETW014_600x600','','inherit','open','open','','etw014_600x600','','','2013-09-11 21:59:47','2013-09-11 19:59:47','',222,'http://localhost/constructions-incongrues/org.incongru.ruedesgardes/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/ETW014_600x600.jpg',0,'attac